2025-01-02 13:14:15 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Discuss\Post:Insert {"timestamp":1735823655,"user_id":null,"user_ip":"23.105.5.108","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (X11; Fedora; Linux x86_64; rv:114.0) Gecko\/20100101 Firefox\/114.0","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Discuss\\Post","entity_data":{"id":10386,"__foreign_props":[],"parent_id":"0","cat_id":"4","project_id":"1656","nick":"Oscar","topic":"Revolutionize Your Instagram Game with AI-Powered Growth","content":"Get more leads for your studioatrium.pl website by using AI on Instagram. If you're looking to drive more traffic, generate leads, and grow your brand's reach, you can get more information and start a free trial here: https:\/\/cutt.ly\/ie1D0Oh6\r\n\r\nThis is an AI-powered Instagram growth service that:\r\n-Increases followers with targeted, high-quality audiences.\r\n-Boosts engagement through smart AI algorithms.\r\n-Targets users based on hashtags and accounts they follow. \r\n-Saves you time by automating tedious Instagram tasks.\r\n\r\nOur service focuses on real, organic growth\u2014no bots, no fake followers. It\u2019s perfect for brands like yours that want to turn Instagram into a lead generation powerhouse. Better yet, our service is provided on a month-by-month subscription basis so you can cancel any time you like. No contracts and a 7 day free trial.","create_date":"2025-01-02 13:14:15","modify_date":"2025-01-02 13:14:15","status":"published","is_moderated":0,"attachments":[],"_uid":2658863},"entity_changes":false}
